column2: SELECT TOP #  p.ObjID as ObjID,  p.cModelMag_u as Mag_u,  p.cModelMag_g as Mag_g,  p.cModelMag_r as Mag_r,  p.cModelMag_i as Mag_i,  p.cModelMag_z as Mag_z,  q.z as z,  q.zErr as zErr,  q.bestFitTemplateID as TemplateID  from DR1#.GalaxyTag p JOIN DR1#.Photoz q on p.ObjID=q.ObjID
